      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. Can you actually write out a couple of paragraphs for the introduction and the first main point? I want it to sound really authoritative, like it's not just \"one way to look at it\" but actually explaining why the meritocracy argument is basically just a myth used to justify the status quo.",
